{"tid":518325,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"情懷玩砸了，劇場版《交響詩篇 Hi-Evolution》第一章觀眾劣評如潮","createTime":"2018-01-03T08:16:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-03T17:29:44.000Z","uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"eac29314cf2d2e93682da0c7548981a963dfa5b0","tid":518325,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T08:16:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/%E4%BA%A4%E9%9F%BF%E8%A9%A9%E7%AF%87.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F04%2F%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E9%259F%25BF%25E8%25A9%25A9%25E7%25AF%2587.jpg&d=tPtgdxispHM4pG8INjHj0TANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=2da80033\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/%E4%BA%A4%E9%9F%BF%E8%A9%A9%E7%AF%87.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n劇場版《交響詩篇Hi-Evolution》第一章上星期在日本正式上映，這個三部曲劇場版並非只是總集篇，而是有全新加入的內容以及新的《交響詩篇》世界觀設定<br />\n然而本應該是情懷大作的《交響詩篇Hi-Evolution》上映後迎來的卻是觀眾的劣評如潮，這次情懷玩砸了<br />\n<br />\n目前《交響詩篇High Evolution》<a href=\"http://第一章在雅虎電影還有映畫.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E7%AB%A0%E5%9C%A8%E9%9B%85%E8%99%8E%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1%E9%82%84%E6%9C%89%E6%98%A0%E7%95%AB.com&d=tPtgdxispHM4pG8INjHj0TANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=f29de736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">第一章在雅虎電影還有映畫.com</a> 網站上得到的觀眾評分是2.5、2.6<br />\n根據觀眾的觀後反應，第一章中只有幾分鐘是全新的畫面，剩下的都是TV版已有的畫面，而且舊畫面還是以當年播出時4:3的比例放映，令這部劇場版的魄力減半<br />\n而且劇場版中因為世界觀設定有變化，所以在TV版中的重要角色有一些在劇場版中沒出現<br />\n新的畫面有限，之後幾乎都是使用已有的TV版畫面，本來TV版的同一個場景還被反覆使用，10年前就看夠了，有觀眾認為花1800日元看這部劇場版有種被製作方耍了的感覺<br />\n<br />\n有影評家認為使用已有的TV版動畫畫面再加上全新的世界觀設定，這種手法並不能說是絕對不好<br />\n但這次劇場版的問題在於這麼做了之後，與其說是原創更像是劣化了《交響詩篇》這部作品，如果要這麼做的話必須要超越原版才可以，劇場版有新設定的話也要好好地向觀眾說明才行，但是這次的劇場版剪輯太亂說明不足<br />\n因為是三部曲的劇場版，監督可能希望大家看完三部作品之後再去評價，但是觀眾只能評價現在看到的作品，如果被大多數粉絲批評的話，這就是個失敗作品<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkacger.com/archives/43583\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Farchives%2F43583&d=tPtgdxispHM4pG8INjHj0TANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=27f73263\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkacger.com/archives/43583</a>"},{"pid":"4ae849757cf90d742a8a148508dc40dc30c3776c","tid":518325,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T08:16:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/%E4%BA%A4%E9%9F%BF%E8%A9%A9%E7%AF%87.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F04%2F%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E9%259F%25BF%25E8%25A9%25A9%25E7%25AF%2587.jpg&h=4e1260aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/%E4%BA%A4%E9%9F%BF%E8%A9%A9%E7%AF%87-2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F07%2F%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E9%259F%25BF%25E8%25A9%25A9%25E7%25AF%2587-2.jpg&h=97dabbd7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a6f4195c089ca43c38a174241e7877a3db8ad9c8","tid":518325,"uid":49391,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T08:18:01.000Z","msg":"舊畫面還是以當年播出時4:3的比例放映<br />\n<br />\n咁真係好柒,未試過響戲院睇4:3嘅戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7042980444aacedf1a429a5c94f16905fe1ef94d","tid":518325,"uid":29551,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T08:40:05.000Z","msg":"而且舊畫面還是以當年播出時4:3的比例放映<br />\n<br />\n睇到呢句已經知玩撚完<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"095b45bb9d6415c166191f47b15494c18347a53e","tid":518325,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T08:40:54.000Z","msg":"篇野都好耐下<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1981829d8703fa8c70bc26b755afa09058d71b61","tid":518325,"uid":91931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T08:42:45.000Z","msg":"完全冇意欲睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"895a580067cb7dc98cc85fcd86bfb8a0aa1f1738","tid":518325,"uid":3508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"